Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.86,0:00:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.98,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.75,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.82,0:00:32.16,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.50,0:00:41.60,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.67,0:00:50.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.97,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:56.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.88,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.99,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.06,0:01:16.77,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.97,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.04,0:01:23.24,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.47,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.45,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡終究還是被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.55,0:02:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到戰略偵查部隊\N傳來的魔導聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經在山區\N發現了廢棄公主一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離命運之日還有兩天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了平息眾神的怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.93,0:02:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何一定要除掉廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.83,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把所有巨神像戰車集中到山區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.84,0:02:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#23 有限之物的聖譚曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也可以發動聖戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們希望能夠\N更確實的除掉律法破壞者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用使者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.94,0:03:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉讓您受驚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹的狀況呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是你們沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把廢棄公主帶到城外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.23,0:03:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在不認為她會毀滅世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是專程來跟我告別的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上年紀的人還真是早起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天，我變成16歲以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆太陽會不會照樣升起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上太陽升起來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會變成怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許正在做難吃的早餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.96,0:05:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定會給\N這個世界上的人們帶來麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是任性嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把想活著當作任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天底下要是有這種蠢事那還得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼樣的罪犯都一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算因為那個人的緣故\N死了很多人也一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡、夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯煮好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚您睡的安穩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.09,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很擔心那些傷患的聲音\N會不會太吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷患？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.43,0:06:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在王都災難中受傷的人\N不斷地被送到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有一部分被當作臨時醫院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請佛爾西斯殿下\N去慰問一下他們呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們連治病的錢都沒有\N才會到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣活下來的人\N總有一天會痊癒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多人去世了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要廢棄公主還在這個世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在神的怒火之下受傷的人\N就還會繼續增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，為了拯救萬民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您成為使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在偷笑什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點什麼事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯對我說謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿早餐給他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在笑什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國軍越來越接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況我也只會洗衣服而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，說不定這就是\N妳自己的戰鬥方式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛羅蒂說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有自己的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.07,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直...想要改變這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把這個腐敗的世界給毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不全都是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個世界\N說不定也不算太糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次帶我到妳的村子去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，歡迎來玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊，來玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會請你們吃很多東西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了，我來做就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切絲要切的更細一點\N切細一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥，你很吵耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾肯斯先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐妳也一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他是來傳話的，要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛爾西斯王子說想要見小姐一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛爾西斯王子是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，為什麼這麼突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是想在生日之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟親妹妹見一面的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這種時候才跟我說這些...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是廢棄公主喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.13,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是現在想殺我的\N那個國家的王子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說他是我的哥哥\N我也沒有什麼實際的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到現在才想見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個怎麼樣的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.88,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是國王的話\N應該不會隨便發動戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也一直很關心妳的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定只是想見見妳，確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.93,0:10:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是不是毀滅世界的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須帶著妳的答覆\N回到聖都才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要見的話就要開始準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見的話，我就這樣回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到黃昏的時候給我答覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得人生還真是煩惱多多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.37,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也為了\N騎士道到底是什麼煩惱過嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.78,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道是什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直認為絕對有一種\N任何人都能相信的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.56,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開始覺得\N或許根本就沒有那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我相信王國\N還有瑪烏傑魯教的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.67,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對帕希菲卡來說那就不是正義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.84,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣一來，我變得不知道\N到底什麼該是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我發現到一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實到最後，我只是想要\N保護帕希菲卡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別談我的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望帕希菲卡\N可以跟我談談妳的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？跟你談？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你聊過以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己這麼煩惱\N簡直就像個笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥要是個好人的話就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.85,0:12:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳哥哥看到妳以後\N一定會很喜歡妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.86,0:12:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，那就由我來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去見他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正人生只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇上困難失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也比事後才後悔來的好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐你真是一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那條頭巾\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.58,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是我們第一次見面的時候\N我幫你綁的那一條吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗一洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好在他們的射程距離內呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在天一亮的時候\N發動總攻擊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽下山以後\N我們也開始行動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.21,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不記得喪失記憶時所見過的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.13,0:13:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然帕希菲卡沒有明說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想她應該很喜歡那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.61,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻什麼也不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.01,0:13:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，妳還記得那個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說人類是一種對\N越痛苦的事情越容易忘記的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.59,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為忘記了才能繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在王都的時候真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故意不理妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想把妳\N捲進廢棄公主的事情裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係...已經沒關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐之前說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她身上有種不像平民的氣質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她原本就不是平民嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望她說不去見他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要是說想見自己真正的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有權利阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼才叫作真正呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的妹妹是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情會改變嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥，拉蔻兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想去見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去見我的雙胞胎哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去見他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛爾西斯殿下，您怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.83,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.74,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想呼吸外面的空氣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.81,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發的時候太太給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.69,0:16:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我回去以後拿去種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我太太最喜歡的\N黃色紫羅蘭的種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到一個很好的伴侶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到\N能夠跟我一起過日子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果這東西就成了我的伴侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾兩位長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖都傳來了命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定計劃改變目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，日落的同時開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是要去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾個小時就到明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會祈禱妳平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是...帕希菲卡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡吃什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡吃雞蛋\N應該說是雞蛋料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其特別喜歡吃蛋包飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡吃雞蛋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是雙胞胎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.07,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去讓妳吃了這麼多苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會，不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在妳被當成廢棄公主\N遭到追殺的期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻不能為妳做任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多辛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不完全是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的哥哥和姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是一群很善良的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.21,0:19:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才見到妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛爾西斯殿下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在瞄準教堂開砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？王子明明也來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.99,0:20:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的形相干涉能力\N說不定會有辦法救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然要花點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓妳礙事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆啊，阻擋一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.41,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他會做到這種地步\N真是個令人高興的失算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟龍機神一起過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我馬上就燒毀王都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神的使者出現了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點開炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛爾西斯殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身為王子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保護民眾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.85,0:22:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少...跟妹妹一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.15,0:22:43.02,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.09,0:22:48.32,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.40,0:22:55.67,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.74,0:23:01.40,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.48,0:23:06.34,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.41,0:23:09.75,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.82,0:23:14.72,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.79,0:23:21.25,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.33,0:23:24.66,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.96,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.03,0:23:34.44,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.51,0:23:41.38,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.72,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.79,0:23:53.59,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被親哥哥刺了一劍的帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.80,0:24:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒看著血流不止的妹妹\N卻完全束手無策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.47,0:24:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂在燒毀王都的威脅之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.34,0:24:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已只好與賽菲莉絲融合\N和秩序守護者展開大戰
